videos.description: Jake Lindsey throws a lob from the top of the key to Jo Lual-Acuil Jr. who flushes it home with two hands.
videos.headline: Baylor's Lual-Acuil rises for alley-oop

videos.description: Tristan Clark anticipates the pass on defense, comes up with a steal and finishes in transition with an easy lay-in.
videos.headline: Clark steals and scores for Baylor

videos.description: Tristan Clark spins in the post and throws down a powerful two-handed flush over two Randall defenders.
videos.headline: Baylor's Clark dunks on two defenders
